snippet.title: Pro Football - Development Preview 3
snippet.description:
Pro Football - Development Preview 3

Hello dear users, this is the third video of the development phase of Pro Football, a game inspired on the football managers from 90s. Our goal is to bring back the essence and excitement of the original game while incorporating modern gameplay mechanics and features. Pro Football is designed for fans of strategic sports management games, offering a deep and engaging experience without the need for real player or club licenses. Instead, you'll dive into a world of randomized players and clubs or have the option to load external databases with unique player names and club identities.

v0.0.16-dev
